  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;The advertisement by reason of their number, siting, scale and method of illumination is considered to, add unnecessary clutter,&amp;nbsp;adversely affect the historic significance of the surrounding buildings and fail to preserve or enhance the the character and appearance of the Hoxton Street Conservation Area.&amp;nbsp;As such, the proposal is contrary to policies LP3(Designated Heritage Assets) and LP7(Advertisements) of the Hackney Local Plan LP33 (2020) and policies D4(Delivering good design) and HC1(Heritage and growth) of the London Plan (2021).&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;"
